(22, 'apple', '[\"red\", \"fruit\"]', 'A red apple is a type of fruit known for its vibrant red skin, which can range from bright to deep red tones. It typically has a round shape with a small stem at the top. The interior flesh is crisp and juicy, usually with a sweet-tart flavor that varies depending on the specific variety. Red apples are commonly used in both raw and cooked forms, being a popular choice for snacks, salads, baking, and juices. They are also celebrated for their nutritional benefits, including a good source of dietary fiber and vitamin C.', 'https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1101017132482957363/1176561982846029874/365cent_apple_amazon_product_image_realistic_white_background_2417a6f6-8759-41e2-b480-0637aec4a01e.png?ex=656f51bc&is=655cdcbc&hm=1e3ab318331ab437aafad157b3f1d5801f68771e44b40b224edba2c2140fc25d&'),
(89, 'Vintage White Wooden Executive Desk', '[\"furniture\",\"desk\",\"office furniture\",\"executive desk\",\"wooden desk\",\"vintage style\",\"white desk\",\"home office\",\"storage\",\"\"]', 'A spacious and sturdy desk designed for a home office or executive workspace. Featuring a classic white finish with a contrasting dark tabletop, this desk offers ample storage with its multiple drawers, including file drawers, utility drawers, a center drawer, and a cabinet. The elegant metal pulls add a touch of sophistication, while the solid construction and detailed paneling give a timeless look. Designed for functionality and style, this desk would be a perfect addition to any office or study.', 'https://imgs.search.brave.com/hw4Ij1o8UHA58fCGE-6LaBHYzcnymUUwOinC62-1b4g/rs:fit:860:0:0/g:ce/aHR0cHM6Ly9pbWFn/ZXJlc2l6ZXIuZnVy/bml0dXJlZGVhbGVy/Lm5ldC9pbWcvcmVt/b3RlL2ltYWdlcy5m/dXJuaXR1cmVkZWFs/ZXIubmV0L2ltZy9w/cm9kdWN0cy9hc3Bl/bmhvbWUvY29sb3Iv/Y2FyYXdheS0tMzA0/NTg4MzM5X2kyNDgt/MzAzLWIxLmpwZz93/aWR0aD00NTAmaGVp/Z2h0PTQ1MCZzY2Fs/ZT1ib3RoJnRyaW0u/dGhyZXNob2xkPTIw'),
(91, 'Modern Black Writing Desk', '[\"furniture\",\"desk\",\"writing desk\",\"black\",\"modern\",\"minimalist\",\"home office\",\"study furniture\",\"wood\",\"\"]', 'A contemporary writing desk with a sleek black finish, featuring a clean, minimalist design with a single gold-finished drawer pull on the front. Designed for both functionality and style, it fits well in home offices, study areas, or as a statement piece in living spaces.', 'https://imgs.search.brave.com/inL98a3OXRejDym85WwHoIpiTekpOtmJe8HMMYZ3Xnw/rs:fit:860:0:0/g:'),
(92, 'Modern Wooden Dining Chair', '[\"furniture\",\"chair\",\"wooden\",\"modern\",\"dining room\",\"minimalist\",\"natural finish\",\"\"]', 'A sleek, contemporary dining chair crafted from high-quality wood with a natural finish. The design features clean lines and a minimalist aesthetic, making it a versatile addition to any modern dining room or kitchen space. Its sturdy construction ensures durability while providing a comfortable seating experience.', 'https://imgs.search.brave.com/8MqziKwj1zI5smBSxD-7f0oKBEC2g0HJ9o-_GAUnH-4/rs:fit:860:0:0/g:ce/aHR0cHM6Ly9tZWRp/YS5pc3RvY2twaG90/by5jb20vaWQvMTIz/NTQwOTA5OC9waG90/by93b29kZW4tY2hh/aXIuanBnP3M9NjEy/eDYxMiZ3PTAmaz0y/MCZjPVRWcGgwWVZf/bWRqbkpVN2lKdFdC/UUo5cnIyQVIzMk04/UWZsc0I4NE1Ld289'),
