(96, 'Clear Glass Water Bottle', '[\"water bottle\",\"glass\",\"reusable\",\"eco-friendly\",\"portable\",\"transparent\",\"hydration\",\"drinkware\",\"\"]', 'This elegant clear glass water bottle features a sleek design with a transparent body and a convenient carrying loop integrated into the screw-on lid. It is a reusable and eco-friendly choice for staying hydrated on the go.', 'https://imgs.search.brave.com/nfVhbNlr3bFw4Q5pQMB6tsp4FKquZb5eFhpCqDSbayk/rs:fit:860:0:0/g:ce/aHR0cHM6Ly9raW50/by1jYW5hZGEuY2Ev/Y2RuL3Nob3AvcHJv/ZHVjdHMva2ludG9f/d2F0ZXJfYm90dGxl/Xy1fMjAzOTFfLV81/MDBtbF8tX2NsZWFy/X2IyMDVjMjBmLTE0/ODUtNDVmYS04ZjFl/LWE5ZDM5ZDlmYTJi/Ml8xMDAweC5qcGc_/dj0xNjEzNTg5MTIz'),
(97, 'Insulated Water Bottles', '[\"water bottles\",\"insulated\",\"travel\",\"outdoors\",\"beverage container\",\"sleek design\",\"PURIST\",\"\"]', 'A set of two insulated water bottles designed to keep beverages at the desired temperature for extended periods. One bottle is yellow with a black flip-top lid, and the other is dark blue with a stainless steel twist-off lid and a branded logo that says PURIST at the bottom. Both bottles feature a modern, sleek design suitable for travel, outdoor activities, and everyday use.', 'https://imgs.search.brave.com/NHuFROO4PDv8GSxVpnCrpfYzKPsjNgUbD7FEOHKFDns/rs:fit:860:0:0/g:ce/aHR0cHM6Ly9jZG4u/dGhld2lyZWN1dHRl/ci5jb20vd3AtY29u/dGVudC9tZWRpYS8y/MDIwLzEwL3dhdGVy/Ym90dGxlcy0yMDQ4/cHgtMDEyMjYuanBn/P2F1dG89d2VicCZx/dWFsaXR5PTc1Jndp/ZHRoPTEwMjQ'),
(98, 'HydroJug Water Bottle', '[\"water bottle\",\"hydration\",\"fitness\",\"durable\",\"teal-green\",\"HydroJug\",\"large capacity\",\"\"]', 'This is a high-capacity, teal-green HydroJug water bottle designed for on-the-go hydration. Featuring a durable structure with an integrated handle, it is ideal for fitness enthusiasts and anyone needing sufficient water intake during the day. The bottle boasts a sleek design with a prominent logo, making it a stylish and practical choice for staying hydrated.', 'https://imgs.search.brave.com/Zn-KRhm0VzFtF92Gl42wK2hSYLZPgFDbffiqjI1ynZ0/rs:fit:860:0:0/g:ce/aHR0cHM6Ly9oaXBz/LmhlYXJzdGFwcHMu/Y29tL3ZhZGVyLXBy/b2QuczMuYW1hem9u/YXdzLmNvbS8xNjY5/MDcyNDY0LTMxc296/ZG9xeEhMLl9TTDUw/MF8uanBnP2Nyb3A9/MXh3OjEuMDB4aDtj/ZW50ZXIsdG9wJnJl/c2l6ZT05ODA6Kg'),
