(109, 'Modern Portable Laptop', '[\"laptop\",\"computer\",\"technology\",\"portable\",\"lightweight\",\"sleek\",\"modern\",\"minimalist\",\"\"]', 'This is a sleek and stylish portable laptop featuring a slim profile and a minimalist design with a large trackpad, backlit keyboard, and the iconic logo on its lid. The laptop is depicted in a floating position suggesting its lightweight and easy-to-carry nature. Its set against a soft turquoise background that provides a contrasting backdrop, amplifying the devices premium and contemporary aesthetic.', 'https://imgs.search.brave.com/JN8V-JvR6e1uaZF1iT5CFFuwnLMazAJ8LH2hPi5L0eI/rs:fit:860:0:0/g:ce/aHR0cHM6Ly9tZWRp/YS5nZXR0eWltYWdl/cy5jb20vaWQvMTIz/NTcyODkwMy9waG90/by9hLTEzLWluY2gt/YXBwbGUtbWFjYm9v/ay1wcm8tbGFwdG9w/LWNvbXB1dGVyLXRh/a2VuLW9uLWphbnVh/cnktMjAtMjAyMS5q/cGc_cz02MTJ4NjEy/Jnc9MCZrPTIwJmM9/aFlSYnYxZThCNlk5/TWF2UVpfX29ibGhr/S0hUbVVyS2pXc0hs/QTNxZHppWT0'),
(110, 'Fresh Watermelon', '[\"fruit\",\"ripe\",\"fresh\",\"watermelon\",\"refreshing\",\"juicy\",\"summer\",\"\"]', 'A ripe, juicy watermelon with distinctive dark green skin marked by lighter green stripes. The surface appears to be slightly dewy, suggesting freshness. Perfect for a refreshing snack or fruit salad on a hot day.', 'https://imgs.search.brave.com/_k8xTPEh-Otb7blSl2CcK-oR17gZpSMDKUB_dmFG5no/rs:fit:860:0:0/g:ce/aHR0cHM6Ly9pbWFn/ZXMucGV4ZWxzLmNv/bS9waG90b3MvMTMx/MzI2Ny9wZXhlbHMt/cGhvdG8tMTMxMzI2/Ny5qcGVnP2F1dG89/Y29tcHJlc3MmY3M9/dGlueXNyZ2ImZHBy/PTEmdz01MDA'),
(111, 'Fresh Strawberries', '[\"fruit\",\"berries\",\"strawberries\",\"fresh produce\",\"healthy\",\"vitamin C\",\"diet\",\"\"]', 'A vibrant collection of ripe strawberries featuring a rich red color and fresh green stems. The berries appear juicy and are commonly consumed fresh, used in desserts, or preserved in jams.', 'https://imgs.search.brave.com/yH2AFtrI2OD9Y0EJMMCMk-ppMw7gAvU_yZrHSrfTQRY/rs:fit:860:0:0/g:ce/aHR0cHM6Ly9pbWFn/ZXMucGV4ZWxzLmNv/bS9waG90b3MvNDYx/NzQvc3RyYXdiZXJy/aWVzLWJlcnJpZXMt/ZnJ1aXQtZnJlc2hu/ZXNzLTQ2MTc0Lmpw/ZWc_YXV0bz1jb21w/cmVzcyZjcz10aW55/c3JnYiZkcHI9MSZ3/PTUwMA'),
(113, 'RGB Gaming Mouse', '[\"gaming\",\"mouse\",\"RGB\",\"ergonomic\",\"programmable\",\"precision\",\"peripheral\",\"PC\",\"accessory\",\"\"]', 'A high-precision RGB gaming mouse with customizable lighting. It features an ergonomic design, multiple programmable buttons, and a textured grip for enhanced control. Suitable for gamers seeking a combination of aesthetics and performance.', 'https://imgs.search.brave.com/NFj7Yca-7EjcIv2k0B68OHcGMuD2uW-qo-gIDTzDfQ4/rs:fit:860:0:0/g:ce/aHR0cHM6Ly90My5m/dGNkbi5uZXQvanBn/LzA1Lzg5LzkwLzc2/LzM2MF9GXzU4OTkw/NzYwM191eEJtMzhM/Y0FObEtqQkZucEY4/MnZaMW5OUGpVQ0tr/Si5qcGc'),
(114, 'Wireless Bluetooth Earbuds', '[\"electronics\",\"audio\",\"wireless earbuds\",\"Bluetooth\",\"portable\",\"\"]', 'A sleek pair of wireless Bluetooth earbuds that come with a compact charging case. Designed for easy connectivity and long-lasting battery life, they offer high-quality audio experience with the convenience of no cables. Ideal for on-the-go music, calls, and multimedia enjoyment.', 'data:image/jpeg;base64,'),
(115, 'Red & Black Wireless Gaming Controller', '[\"gaming\",\"controller\",\"wireless\",\"red\",\"black\",\"textured grip\",\"console accessory\",\"\"]', 'This is a wireless gaming controller compatible with a specific gaming console, featuring a sleek red and black design. It includes standard buttons and joysticks for gameplay, along with textured grip on the handles for comfortable long-term play. This controller is perfect for gamers looking to enhance their gaming experience with a responsive and visually striking accessory.', 'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/shopping?q=tbn:ANd9GcRIyu74r375FkNA5VuCyoFs7TNdI7vXp4gBWS1agcDHlX0i62FnYDFoCzgXzdWCBgv8LdI2HOHBS1K-WpuXGWFCGquuYdoXLxausqW7HPZ28LFk_F709wJpumg23FGwJuFSo-ME6dr_Sg&usqp=CAc'),
(120, 'Sleek Modern Laptop', '[\"laptop\",\"technology\",\"electronics\",\"portable\",\"modern\",\"minimalist\",\"professional\",\"student\",\"high-performance\",\"multimedia\",\"\"]', 'A modern, lightweight laptop with a minimalist design, featuring a large trackpad and an illuminated keyboard. It is ideal for professionals and students who need a portable, high-performance computer for everyday tasks and multimedia activities.', 'https://imgs.search.brave.com/JN8V-JvR6e1uaZF1iT5CFFuwnLMazAJ8LH2hPi5L0eI/rs:fit:860:0:0/g:ce/aHR0cHM6Ly9tZWRp/YS5nZXR0eWltYWdl/cy5jb20vaWQvMTIz/NTcyODkwMy9waG90/by9hLTEzLWluY2gt/YXBwbGUtbWFjYm9v/ay1wcm8tbGFwdG9w/LWNvbXB1dGVyLXRh/a2VuLW9uLWphbnVh/cnktMjAtMjAyMS5q/cGc_cz02MTJ4NjEy/Jnc9MCZrPTIwJmM9/aFlSYnYxZThCNlk5/TWF2UVpfX29ibGhr/S0hUbVVyS2pXc0hs/QTNxZHppWT0'),
(121, 'Samsung Smartphone', '[\"smartphone\",\"Samsung\",\"triple camera\",\"technology\",\"mobile device\",\"electronics\",\"\"]', 'A modern Samsung smartphone featuring a sleek design with a triple rear camera setup and the Samsung logo engraved on the back. Resting against a blue fabric background, the device showcases a muted greenish-gray color and a minimalistic aesthetic.', 'https://images.hindustantimes.com/tech/img/2023/02/14/960x540/SG2_1676367813910_1676367826859_1676367826859.jpg'),
(123, 'Samsung Smartphone', '[\"smartphone\",\"Samsung\",\"electronics\",\"mobile device\",\"camera phone\",\"technology\",\"gadget\",\"\"]', 'The image shows a modern Samsung smartphone with a sleek silver design, featuring a triple-lens rear camera setup and an LED flash. The device boasts a clean, minimalist aesthetic and seems to offer a premium handfeel.', 'https://www.digitaltrends.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/galaxy-s22-angled-shot.jpg?p=1'),
(124, 'Type-C Emergency Button Device', '[\"emergency\",\"button\",\"portable\",\"Type-C\",\"USB\",\"device\",\"safety\",\"compact\",\"trigger\",\"alert\",\"on-the-go\",\"\"]', 'A portable emergency device with a prominent red button, designed to connect via a Type-C USB port. The device appears to be a compact solution intended for users to quickly trigger a specific action or send an alert through a connected system. Its portable nature and sturdy strap suggest it can be conveniently attached to accessories or carried on-the-go.', 'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRNJz7D-O-Id4abMGPOPjkw5Esm5-3FwJQexA&usqp=CAU'),
(125, 'Among Us Impostor Edition - Nintendo Switch', '[\"video game\",\"Nintendo Switch\",\"Among Us\",\"Impostor Edition\",\"multiplayer\",\"social deduction\",\"collectible\",\"\"]', 'This is a special edition box set of the popular multiplayer game Among Us, designed specifically for the Nintendo Switch gaming console. The package, titled Impostor Edition, includes the base game along with additional content and collectibles tailored for fans of the highly engaging social deduction game. The box features a sleek design with the recognizable crewmate character and the iconic imposter red shhh logo. Great for both collectors and players seeking the complete Among Us experience on the Switch.', 'https://i5.walmartimages.ca/images/Enlarge/912/714/6000203912714.jpg?odnHeight=612&odnWidth=612&odnBg=FFFFFF'),
(126, 'Foldable Smartphone', '[\"electronics\",\"smartphone\",\"foldable\",\"technology\",\"AMOLED\",\"mobile device\",\"\"]', 'A state-of-the-art foldable smartphone featuring a dynamic AMOLED display that folds in the middle for enhanced portability. It includes multiple applications pre-installed, such as app stores and various proprietary services. The device boasts a seamless hinge mechanism, allowing it to open like a book and offer a large screen experience, switching from a traditional smartphone form factor to a tablet-like display.', 'https://www.cnet.com/a/img/resize/d366c841bece02857af6657da07bef269c6ba76a/hub/2022/08/24/9f399223-b1b8-409d-b7db-db91829fd896/samsung-galaxy-z-fold-4-6662.jpg?auto=webp&fit=crop&height=1200&width=1200'),
(127, 'Modern Flip Smartphone', '[\"smartphone\",\"flip phone\",\"folding screen\",\"modern technology\",\"portable\",\"innovative design\",\"high-resolution display\",\"dual screen\",\"compact\",\"elegance\",\"\"]', 'This sleek, modern flip smartphone features a versatile folding screen that allows for compact storage and a large display when opened. The design showcases a hinge mechanism that enables the screen to fold smoothly, maintaining a seamless image across the bend. With both external and internal screens, the device allows users to check notifications and perform basic tasks without opening the clamshell, while offering a spacious touchscreen for full smartphone capabilities when unfolded. The phones crisp display projects vibrant images and includes a front-facing camera for video calls or selfies. Crafted for those who appreciate innovative technology wrapped in a stylish, portable form factor, this smartphone embodies the evolution of mobile devices with its blend of functionality and elegance.', 'https://www.cnet.com/a/img/hub/2022/08/10/1360fa66-eef7-46bb-873b-6877eb16b52f/screen-shot-2022-08-10-at-6-06-39-am.jpg'),
(128, 'Huawei Mate X2 Concept', '[\"smartphone\",\"Huawei\",\"Mate X2\",\"concept\",\"foldable phone\",\"stylus\",\"technology\",\"gadget\",\"\"]', 'An artistic representation of the Huawei Mate X2, showcasing a futuristic foldable smartphone design with an edge-to-edge display. This concept emphasizes a sleek form factor with a vivid display, and includes a stylus for enhanced productivity.', 'https://www.notebookcheck.net/fileadmin/Notebooks/News/_nc3/safe_image.jpg'),
(129, 'Folding Smartphone Display', '[\"technology\",\"smartphone\",\"folding screen\",\"mobile device\",\"innovation\",\"electronics expo\",\"Huawei\",\"\"]', 'A cutting-edge folding smartphone prominently displayed at a technology expo. The device showcases a large, vibrant screen with minimal bezels, highlighting its capability to bend without a visible hinge separation. The screen displays a colorful interface with various application icons, suggesting advanced software integration and user-friendly design.', 'https://www.notebookcheck.net/fileadmin/_processed_/4/b/csm_IMG_20200224_16225562_9c311b7bdd.jpg'),
