(164, 'DSLR Cameras', '[\"photography\",\"camera\",\"DSLR\",\"Nikon\",\"Canon\",\"professional camera\",\"hobby\",\"technology\",\"\"]', 'A pair of professional digital single-lens reflex (DSLR) cameras from leading manufacturers, offering high-resolution image capture, robust build quality, and a wide range of features designed for both amateur and professional photographers. The cameras come with branded lenses and are ideal for various photography needs from landscape to portrait.', 'https://imgs.search.brave.com/rf70nNsGqh7s078DAo4XubDG3q4yPUT5zE7F78F1zXg/rs:fit:860:0:0/g:ce/aHR0cHM6Ly9waXNj/ZXMuYmJ5c3RhdGlj/LmNvbS9pbWFnZTIv/QmVzdEJ1eV9VUy9k/YW0vU09MLTExMjcw/MC1kZXB0LWRzbHJf/REVSLTE0NDAxZjk5/LWY2OTAtNGRkYi04/YWRlLTQ4MmJlMjg2/MzcyOC5qcGc7bWF4/SGVpZ2h0PTM2MDtt/YXhXaWR0aD01MzA'),
(165, 'Western University Hoodie', '[\"apparel\",\"hoodie\",\"university merchandise\",\"casual wear\",\"Western University\",\"college gear\",\"\"]', 'A comfortable and stylish white hoodie featuring the Western University logo, perfect for students, alumni, or fans of the institution. The hoodie is designed with a large font stating Western and the university crest below. Ideal for casual wear or collegiate events.', 'https://bookstore.uwo.ca/files/styles/product_teaser_lg/public/product-images/52219201-web.jpg?itok=l17Sof9d'),
(166, 'Western MOM Purple Hoodie', '[\"hoodie\",\"outerwear\",\"purple\",\"casual\",\"zipper\",\"unisex\",\"pockets\",\"logo\",\"comfort\",\"\"]', 'This comfortable hoodie features a rich purple hue with a Western MOM logo on the upper left chest. The design includes a drawstring hood, a full zipper front, and split kangaroo pockets. Its casual and warm design makes it perfect for daily wear or sporting events.', 'https://bookstore.uwo.ca/files/styles/product_teaser_lg/public/product-images/52227301-web.jpg?itok=PxOZjlOz');
