(171, 'Professional DSLR Camera', '[\"camera\",\"DSLR\",\"professional photography\",\"high-resolution\",\"manual settings\",\"automatic settings\",\"large aperture\",\"quality picture\",\"electronic\",\"\"]', 'A high-resolution professional digital single-lens reflex (DSLR) camera, featured with a large aperture lens for superior picture quality. Designed for seasoned photographers, it offers manual and automatic settings, providing versatility in various shooting conditions.', 'https://imgs.search.brave.com/4g2rkJbO5e1LXCR7GH35wKX608lPg3qbgyTM2I_o3ow/rs:fit:500:0:0/g:ce/aHR0cHM6Ly9tZWRp/YS5nZXR0eWltYWdl/cy5jb20vaWQvMTU3/MjkyMjQ1L3Bob3Rv/L2NhbWVyYS1zbHIu/anBnP3M9NjEyeDYx/MiZ3PTAmaz0yMCZj/PXB0UjIxcEE3Y1JV/VERIbklYd0hmMUs3/VzI3WnpaZ3ZUUEsz/WmJfenp3TkU9'),
